OL,4,Cand burning arranged marriage bride
OL,6,FA man has been jailed along with his
OL,7,Fparents after his wife was forced to
OL,8,Ftake medication and doused with a
OL,9,Fcorrosive substance, leaving her in a
OL,10,Fpersistent vegetative state from which
OL,11,Fshe will never recover.
OL,13,FAmbreen Fatima Sheikh was 30 when she
OL,14,Fwas given the anti-diabetes drug
OL,15,Fglimepiride, which induced
OL,16,Fcatastrophic brain injury, after she
OL,17,Fwas brought to the UK from Pakistan
OL,18,Ffollowing an arranged marriage, heard.
