OL,6,FThe trial heard there had then been a
OL,7,Ftwo to three delay before the family
OL,8,Fcalled an ambulance after she
OL,9,Fcollapsed, which may have exacerbated
OL,10,Fher brain injury.
OL,12,FMrs Sheikh was also doused in a
OL,13,Fcaustic substance at the family home
OL,14,Fin , probably some kind of cleaning
OL,15,Ffluid, as she was abused in the house
OL,16,Fin the days leading up to her
OL,17,Fadmission to hospital on 1 August 2015.
OL,19,FAsgar Sheikh, 31, his father Khalid,
OL,20,F55, mother Shabnam, 52, and sister
OL,21,FShagufa, 29, were in December.
