OL,6,FAsgar, Shabnam and Shagufa Sheikh were
OL,7,Falso found guilty of doing an act
OL,8,Fintending to pervert the course of
OL,9,Fjustice.
OL,11,FAll four defendants plus Asgar and
OL,12,FShagufa's brother, Sakalyne Sheikh,
OL,13,F25, were found guilty of conspiracy to
OL,14,Fpervert the course of justice.
OL,16,FOnly the month before Mrs Sheikh's
OL,17,Fadmission to hospital, two police
OL,18,Fofficers had visited the home
OL,19,Ffollowing concerns for her welfare,
OL,20,Fbut they reported her as being fit and
OL,21,Fwell.
