OL,4,Cand burning arranged marriage bride
OL,6,FHowever, Judge Mrs Justice Lambert
OL,7,Fsaid she attached "little weight to
OL,8,Fthat assessment" because Mrs Sheikh
OL,9,Fspoke little English and her father-in-
OL,10,Flaw was present during the visit.
OL,12,FIt was initially thought Mrs Sheikh,
OL,13,Fwho is now 39, would die but, when her
OL,14,Fventilator was turned off in hospital,
OL,15,Fshe began to breathe for herself.
OL,17,FThe court heard that she has been left
OL,18,Funaware of herself or her environment,
OL,19,Fwithout motor response or response to
OL,20,Fpain, and will never recover.
