OL,3,CHusband and parents jailed for abusing
OL,4,Cand burning arranged marriage bride
OL,6,FProsecutors said she only survives by
OL,7,Fbeing fed through a tube and will
OL,8,Feventually die as a consequence of
OL,9,Fwhat happened to her, although this
OL,10,Fmay not happen for many years.
OL,12,FJudge Lambert said: "It is difficult
OL,13,Fto imagine a more serious injury,
OL,14,Fshort of death."
OL,16,FThe court heard that Mrs Sheikh came
OL,17,Fto the family's home in Clara Steet,
OL,18,FHuddersfield, in 2014 after an earlier
OL,19,Farranged marriage with Asgar in
OL,20,FPakistan.
