OL,6,FThe judge said she rarely left the
OL,7,Fhouse and never by herself. She had no
OL,8,Findependent income, no friends in the
OL,9,FUK and could speak only a little
OL,10,FEnglish.
OL,12,FNone of the family gave evidence in
OL,13,Fcourt and the judge said she could not
OL,14,Fsay for sure when the abuse began.
OL,16,FThe trial heard evidence that, soon
OL,17,Fafter Ms Sheikh arrived in the UK, the
OL,18,Ffamily were not happy with her
OL,19,Fhousework and chores, and Khalid
OL,20,FSheikh had suggested she should be
OL,21,Fsent back to Pakistan.
