OL,6,FJudge Lambert said she did not know
OL,7,Fwho administered the corrosive
OL,8,Fsubstance, which left severe burns on
OL,9,FMs Sheikh's lower back, bottom and
OL,10,Fright ear, and must have left her in
OL,11,Fconsiderable and lasting pain.
OL,13,FAnd she said she did not know who
OL,14,F"tricked or forced" her to take the
OL,15,Fglimepiride, which was prescribed to
OL,16,FShabnam Sheikh and is extremely
OL,17,Fdangerous to non-diabetics, even in
OL,18,Fsmall doses.
