OL,6,FThe judge decided there was a two to
OL,7,Fthree-day delay between Ms Sheikh
OL,8,Ffalling unconscious and the family
OL,9,Fcalling an ambulance, during which she
OL,10,Fbecame highly dehydrated and inhaled
OL,11,Ffluids which may have exacerbated her
OL,12,Fbrain injury.
OL,14,FEven when the family called 999, they
OL,15,Flied about what had happened to her.
