OL,6,FShe was in good health before her
OL,7,Fcollapse and there was some evidence
OL,8,Fthat she was a teacher in Pakistan,
OL,9,Fthe court heard.
OL,11,FOne witness said she was "intelligent,
OL,12,Fbright, ambitious and happy-go-lucky"
OL,13,Fbefore she moved to the UK, and the
OL,14,Fjudge said she was someone who would
OL,15,F"light up a room".
OL,17,FThe judge said Mrs Sheikh's father is
OL,18,Fnow dead and her mother is in poor
OL,19,Fhealth in Pakistan. She has seven
OL,20,Fsiblings and one of her brothers has
OL,21,Fbeen over to visit her.
