OL,6,FThe offence of allowing a vulnerable
OL,7,Fadult to suffer physical harm carried
OL,8,Fa maximum sentence of 10 years in
OL,9,Fprison at the time of the offence but
OL,10,Fthis has since been increased by
OL,11,FParliament to 14 years.
OL,13,FAsgar, Khalid and Shabnam Sheikh were
OL,14,Fall jailed for seven years and nine
OL,15,Fmonths.
OL,17,FShagufa Sheikh was given an 18-month
OL,18,Fsentence, suspended for two years,
OL,19,Fwhile Sakalayne Sheikh was given a six-
OL,20,Fmonth sentence, also suspended for two
OL,21,Fyears.
